        Real work, <span class="text-grad">measured</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section__lead">Named clients, real roles, real timelines — documented SEO, content and social work across India, Dubai and the USA. Every number below counts up from real output.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- (A) COUNT-UP STATS (money-green) -->
    <ul class="stats-bar reveal" role="list">
      <li class="stat stats-bar__item">
        <span class="stats-bar__glow" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="stat__num" data-count="36" data-suffix="+">36+</span>
